name: Looking At Rorschachs
description:
After long discussions with good old bandmates, sleepless nights of recordings and mixing and a full time job besides it's finally done! 
"Looking At Rorschachs" was created from February - October '11 and waits for a spin!

Limited 1st Edition with a blue "glow in the dark" compact disc. Every CD ist handmade.

name: This Is A Record By William E.
description:

released 07 February 2011 
William E.: Vocals, guitar, bass, percussion, gameboy programming and all the other stuff you hear on the album. Furthermore songwriting, lyrics, recording and so on. 
Computer voice on "This Is A Record By William E." taken from Mac OS VoiceOver, drum loop based on Roland TR-808 drum computer.
